to a woman -- or any woman, really -- but that it doesn't mean you have to be someone else completely.   If you have a secret "dorky" hobby, don't be afraid to tell her about it if it means a lot to you. Let her see the best qualities that your other friends see. The friends who are your age must like you for some reason, so don't hide your strongest qualities completely.  

